Dialogue: 0,00:00:02.04,00:00:10.05,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:00:10.05,00:00:16.06,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ ひからびた言葉をつないで
Dialogue: 0,00:00:16.06,00:00:20.57,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ それでも僕等シンプルな
Dialogue: 0,00:00:20.57,00:00:24.58,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 想いを伝えたいだけなの
Dialogue: 0,00:00:24.58,00:00:30.59,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 吹き抜けるくすんだあの日の風は
Dialogue: 0,00:00:30.59,00:00:35.10,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 昨日の廃虚に打ち捨てて
Dialogue: 0,00:00:35.10,00:00:40.11,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 君と笑う 今を生きるのだ
Dialogue: 0,00:00:40.11,00:00:44.62,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ それでもあの出来事が
Dialogue: 0,00:00:44.62,00:00:49.13,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 君を苦しめるだろ？
Dialogue: 0,00:00:49.13,00:00:52.64,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ だからこそサヨナラなんだ
Dialogue: 0,00:00:52.64,00:00:56.08,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ このまま何も残らずに
Dialogue: 0,00:00:56.08,00:00:59.58,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ あなたと分かち合うだけ
Dialogue: 0,00:00:59.58,00:01:02.59,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ やがて僕等は
Dialogue: 0,00:01:02.59,00:01:06.60,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ それが全てだと気がついて
Dialogue: 0,00:01:06.60,00:01:10.11,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 悲しみは頬を伝って
Dialogue: 0,00:01:10.11,00:01:13.61,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 涙の河になるだけ
Dialogue: 0,00:01:13.61,00:01:19.62,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 揺れる想いは強い渦になって
Dialogue: 0,00:01:19.62,00:01:24.13,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 溶け合うのよ
Dialogue: 0,00:01:31.14,00:01:33.64,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｻｽｹ)《火[外:99C09079206BA433E50523B592C8055A] 豪火球の術！》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.29,0:01:33.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Estilo Fogo! Jutsu Bola de Fogo!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:33.64,00:01:38.65,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:01:38.65,00:01:42.16,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《何だ？ あの術は！》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:41.83,Italics,,0,0,0,,Que Jutsu é esse?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:42.16,00:01:46.67,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:01:46.67,00:01:48.67,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,くそが！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.27,0:01:48.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:48.67,00:01:50.61,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:01:50.61,00:01:52.61,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,千鳥‼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.77,0:01:52.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Chidori!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:52.61,00:01:54.12,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:01:54.12,00:01:58.12,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾅﾙﾄ)絶対勝つ！いい気になってんじゃねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.27,0:01:56.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu vou vencer, não importa como!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:58.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Não se ache tanto!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:58.12,00:02:00.13,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ダァ～！
Dialogue: 0,00:02:00.13,00:02:01.63,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:02:01.63,00:02:03.63,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｻｸﾗ)やめてよ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:03.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Parem!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:03.63,00:02:11.64,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:12.45,Title,,0,0,0,,Rivais amargos e laços quebrados
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:11.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Rivais amargos e laços quebrados.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:25.68,00:02:28.18,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(鬼童丸)いつ来ても のどかな里だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:28.78,Main,,0,0,0,,A vila está tranquila como sempre.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:28.18,00:02:30.69,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,警備がなってねえぜよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.78,0:02:30.96,Main,,0,0,0,,A segurança é horrível.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:30.69,00:02:33.69,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(左近)フン こんなしけた里の連中なんざ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.84,0:02:37.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Temos só que massacrar todos\Nnessa vila de meia tigela.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:33.69,00:02:37.20,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,サクサク 皆殺しにしちまえばいいんだよ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:02:37.20,00:02:39.21,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(鬼童丸)落ち着けよ 左近｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:39.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Acalme-se, Sakon.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:39.21,00:02:41.71,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(次郎坊)われわれは戦いに来たわけではない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:41.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Não viemos aqui para lutar.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:41.71,00:02:43.71,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(多由也)うるせぇんだよ チキン野郎が｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:44.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Calado, amarelão.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:43.71,00:02:46.72,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ビビったんなら うち帰ってさっさと寝てろ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:45.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Se está com medo,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:47.33,Main,,0,0,0,,deve ir para casa dormir logo.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:46.72,00:02:50.16,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(鬼童丸)だから 落ち着けって言ってんだろ 多由也！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:50.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou falando para\Nse acalmar, Tayuya!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:50.16,00:02:53.17,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,今回の俺たちの仕事は分かってんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:53.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Entende qual é nosso\Ntrabalho dessa vez, não?
Dialogue: 0,00:02:53.17,00:02:57.17,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,行くぜよ スペシャルゲストのエスコートだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:57.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos. Vamos escoltar\Nnosso convidado especial.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:59.18,00:03:01.68,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うお～‼
Dialogue: 0,00:03:01.68,00:03:04.69,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ダァ～‼
Dialogue: 0,00:03:04.69,00:03:06.69,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,やめてよ～‼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:07.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Parem!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:10.20,00:03:13.70,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《くそ！》《止めきれねえ！》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:11.82,Italics,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:13.92,Italics,,0,0,0,,Não consigo parar totalmente!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:24.73,00:03:26.73,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,えっ？《チッ》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:28.24,Italics,,0,0,0,,Kakashi?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:26.73,00:03:29.24,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《カカシ先生!?》
Dialogue: 0,00:03:29.24,00:03:31.74,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)《ナルト 今のは…》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.71,Italics,,0,0,0,,Naruto, o que você fez foi...
Dialogue: 0,00:03:31.74,00:03:34.75,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:03:34.75,00:03:37.25,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(衝突音)
Dialogue: 0,00:03:40.26,00:03:42.77,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)病院の上で 何やってんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:42.88,Main,,0,0,0,,O que vocês estão fazendo\Nno terraço do hospital?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:42.77,00:03:45.77,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ケンカにしちゃちょい やり過ぎでしょうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:47.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Vocês exageraram\Nnessa luta, pessoal.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:45.77,00:03:48.28,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,君たち｡
Dialogue: 0,00:03:48.28,00:03:51.22,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,う…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:03:51.22,00:03:53.22,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うぅ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:03:56.23,00:03:59.23,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)《さっきの術 間違いない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.93,Italics,,0,0,0,,Esse Jutsu de antes, sem dúvidas...
Dialogue: 0,00:03:59.23,00:04:01.23,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,螺旋丸だ》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.50,0:04:00.72,Italics,,0,0,0,,É o Rasengan.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:02.74,00:04:06.25,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,う… うぅ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:04:06.25,00:04:10.25,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)《どうなってる？ 何でナルトのヤツが あの術を…》
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:07.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:10.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Como o Naruto consegue\Nusar aquele Jutsu?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:10.25,00:04:20.26,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:04:21.28,00:04:23.28,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ヘッ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:04:23.28,00:04:26.78,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)ナルトを殺す気だったのか？サスケ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:26.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Pretendia matar o Naruto, Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:28.79,00:04:31.79,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)何 優越感なんかに浸ってる｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:32.20,Main,,0,0,0,,O que está fazendo? Se rendendo\Nao senso de superioridade?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:34.80,00:04:36.81,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)さっきの千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:36.92,Main,,0,0,0,,A força que você aplicou ao Chidori
Dialogue: 0,00:04:36.81,00:04:40.81,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,同じ里の仲間に向ける大きさじゃなかったが…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:40.64,Main,,0,0,0,,não é para atacar um\Ncompanheiro da mesma vila.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:45.83,00:04:49.33,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)何で こんな子どもじみた まねを｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:49.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Que comportamento infantil é esse?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:49.33,00:04:53.34,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)《やはり イタチとの再会が…》
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:52.95,Italics,,0,0,0,,Certamente foi o\Nencontro com o Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:58.28,00:05:00.29,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,フン｡
Dialogue: 0,00:05:07.30,00:05:09.30,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,サスケ君…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:08.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,00:05:13.31,00:05:23.32,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(水がこぼれる音)
Dialogue: 0,00:05:26.34,00:05:28.34,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,くそ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:28.49,Italics,,0,0,0,,Que saco!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:31.85,00:05:36.86,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《ナルト…お前は一体 どこまで…》
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:33.62,Italics,,0,0,0,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:36.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,Qual é o seu limite?!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:43.37,00:05:53.38,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:06:22.39,00:06:28.90,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(泣き声)
Dialogue: 0,00:06:28.90,00:06:30.90,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,カカシ先生…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:30.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Kakashi...
Dialogue: 0,00:06:30.90,00:06:36.41,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(泣き声)
Dialogue: 0,00:06:36.41,00:06:38.42,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)はぁ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:06:38.42,00:06:41.92,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)《チームワークはどこへやら…》
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:41.19,Flashback,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu com\No trabalho em equipe?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:41.92,00:06:45.93,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)あなたですかあの技を教えたのは｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:45.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Foi você que ensinou\Naquela técnica a ele?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:45.93,00:06:48.44,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あの術を扱うには
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:51.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Acho que Naruto ainda é muito\Njovem para aquele Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:48.44,00:06:51.94,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ナルトは まだ幼すぎると思うんですがねぇ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:57.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele poderia ter matado o\NSasuke caso algo desse errado.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:55.38,00:06:58.89,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)下手したらサスケを殺してた｡
Dialogue: 0,00:06:58.89,00:07:02.40,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,例の暁への抵抗手段だとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:02.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que seja uma ferramenta\Npara resistir à Akatsuki,
Dialogue: 0,00:07:02.40,00:07:05.40,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あの術をナルトに教えるなんて｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:05.22,Main,,0,0,0,,imaginar que você ensinaria\Naquilo para o Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,00:07:05.40,00:07:08.41,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(自来也)お互いさまだろのう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:08.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Digo o mesmo.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:08.41,00:07:11.92,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あの千鳥も相当ヤバかったしの｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:11.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Aquele Chidori também\Nestava bem perigoso.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas eu não imaginei
Dialogue: 0,00:07:11.92,00:07:14.42,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,でも まぁ あいつは あの術を
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.29,0:07:18.83,Main,,0,0,0,,que ele era o tipo de criança que usaria\Naquele Jutsu contra um companheiro.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:14.42,00:07:19.43,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,仲間に向けて撃つようなヤツじゃないと思ってたんだがのう｡
Dialogue: 0,00:07:19.43,00:07:24.44,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,それとも よっぽどのことがあのガキとの間にあるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:23.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Ou há algo complicado\Nentre aqueles dois?
Dialogue: 0,00:07:24.44,00:07:27.45,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)まっ いろいろとね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:27.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Bom, muita coisa.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:27.45,00:07:29.45,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,いろいろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Muita coisa?
Dialogue: 0,00:07:29.45,00:07:31.46,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)簡単に言えば
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:34.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Para resumir, a relação deles é como\Na sua e do Orochimaru antigamente.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:31.46,00:07:34.96,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,かつてのあなたと大蛇丸みたいな関係ですかね｡
Dialogue: 0,00:07:38.47,00:07:40.98,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(自来也)ほう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:39.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendo...
Dialogue: 0,00:07:40.98,00:07:42.98,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)あいつにとって サスケは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:45.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Para ele, o Sasuke é um companheiro\Ne rival ao mesmo tempo...
Dialogue: 0,00:07:42.98,00:07:45.48,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,仲間であると同時にライバル｡
Dialogue: 0,00:07:45.48,00:07:50.43,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,まっ 常に対等な存在でありたい男ってことです｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:49.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Bom, é alguém que ele\Nconsidera um igual.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:50.43,00:07:55.44,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,恐らく そのサスケの安い挑発に耐えきれなかったんでしょう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:54.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Acho que ele não conseguiu\Nsuportar a provocação do Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:55.44,00:07:58.94,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,アカデミーの頃からずっと追っかけて…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:58.67,Main,,0,0,0,,E está correndo atrás dele
Dialogue: 0,00:07:58.94,00:08:01.45,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,追っかけてきましたからね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:01.85,Main,,0,0,0,,desde a época da Academia.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:01.45,00:08:04.46,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜ケガはねえかよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:03.84,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Você está machucado,
Dialogue: 0,00:08:04.46,00:08:06.46,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ビビリ君＞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:06.38,Flashback,,0,0,0,,gatinho assustado?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:06.46,00:08:10.47,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜なっ… くっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:11.65,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:10.47,00:08:12.47,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,サスケ～！＞
Dialogue: 0,00:08:12.47,00:08:16.48,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:08:16.48,00:08:19.99,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《お前だけには負けねえ！》
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:19.02,Flashback Italics,,0,0,0,,Não vou perder para você!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:19.99,00:08:23.99,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)今のナルトは私や あなたじゃなく
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:24.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Agora, não é por mim ou por você\Nque ele quer ser reconhecido...
Dialogue: 0,00:08:23.99,00:08:28.50,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,誰からよりも ただ認めてもらいたいんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:26.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Mais do que todo mundo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:30.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele quer ser reconhecido pelo Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:28.50,00:08:31.51,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,サスケにね｡
Dialogue: 0,00:08:31.51,00:08:33.51,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,その一方で
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:33.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Por outro lado,
Dialogue: 0,00:08:33.51,00:08:36.52,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,サスケはナルトの成長スピードを身近で感じて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:38.74,Main,,0,0,0,,o Sasuke está vendo o crescimento do\NNaruto de perto se sente inferior.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:36.52,00:08:38.52,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,劣等感を持っている｡
Dialogue: 0,00:08:38.52,00:08:44.04,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,自分がまるで 成長していないと思い込んでしまうほどに｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:43.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Até um ponto que ele acha que\Nnão está progredindo nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:45.32,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Gatinho assustado?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:44.04,00:08:45.54,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜ビビリ君｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:48.35,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Jutsu Múltiplos Clones das Sombras!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:45.54,00:08:48.04,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,多重影分身の術！
Dialogue: 0,00:08:48.04,00:08:50.48,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,口寄せの術！＞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:50.26,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Jutsu de Invocação!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:50.48,00:08:55.49,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:08:55.49,00:08:59.00,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)ナルトは強くなりましたから｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:58.70,Main,,0,0,0,,O Naruto ficou forte.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:59.00,00:09:01.50,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,それに サスケは…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:01.17,Main,,0,0,0,,E o Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,00:09:01.50,00:09:06.51,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜ある男を必ず 殺すことだ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:06.04,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Eu vou matar um alguém\Nhomem, não importa como.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:06.51,00:09:09.52,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,復しゅうか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:08.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Vingança, é?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:12.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Será que o Itachi está o frustrando?
Dialogue: 0,00:09:09.52,00:09:13.53,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,イタチのヤツがあの子を焦らせてるのか｡
Dialogue: 0,00:09:13.53,00:09:17.03,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)だから サスケはナルトを認めたくない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:16.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Então o Sasuke não quer\Nreconhecer o Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:18.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Se ele o reconhecer,
Dialogue: 0,00:09:17.03,00:09:22.55,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,認めてしまえば 今までの自分を否定してしまいかねない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:22.05,Main,,0,0,0,,ele pode acabar negando\No que fez até agora.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:22.55,00:09:26.55,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,難しいもんですライバルってのはね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:26.06,Main,,0,0,0,,A rivalidade é algo difícil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:29.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso não é legal.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:26.55,00:09:29.56,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あまり いい傾向じゃねえのう｡
Dialogue: 0,00:09:29.56,00:09:33.07,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,少し 説教でもしてやるかのう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:32.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Talvez eu dê uma bronca nele.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:35.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Então deixo o Naruto com você.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:33.07,00:09:35.57,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)では ナルトを お任せします｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:39.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Bom, tenho uma missão. E tem\No negócio do Chidori também...
Dialogue: 0,00:09:35.57,00:09:40.08,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,まっ 私も任務があるし千鳥のこともあるので｡
Dialogue: 0,00:09:42.08,00:09:44.59,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)サクラ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:43.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:44.59,00:09:49.60,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,大丈夫また昔みたいになれるさ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.78,0:09:48.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem. As coisas\Nvoltarão a ser como antes.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:49.60,00:09:52.10,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,元気出せ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:50.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Alegre-se.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:52.10,00:09:54.11,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,じゃあな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:53.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Até mais.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:01.62,00:10:04.63,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《ありがとう カカシ先生》
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:04.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,Obrigada, Kakashi.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:07.64,00:10:10.14,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ナルト｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:09.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,00:10:10.14,00:10:12.64,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,サクラちゃん…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:11.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:18.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Não interfira nos nossos assuntos.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:16.15,00:10:18.65,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,邪魔しないでくれってばよ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:10:32.18,00:10:36.69,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:10:36.69,00:10:38.70,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜うおっ！＞
Dialogue: 0,00:10:38.70,00:10:47.21,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:10:47.21,00:10:50.22,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｲﾀﾁ)＜お前は弱い｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:49.74,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Você é fraco.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:52.14,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Sabe por que é fraco?
Dialogue: 0,00:10:50.22,00:10:52.66,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,なぜ 弱いか？
Dialogue: 0,00:10:52.66,00:10:55.16,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,足りないからだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:55.28,Flashback,,0,0,0,,É porque você não tem
Dialogue: 0,00:10:55.16,00:10:57.67,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,憎しみが＞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:56.81,Flashback,,0,0,0,,ódio o bastante.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:57.67,00:11:01.18,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《今まで 俺は…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:11:00.22,Italics,,0,0,0,,O que eu estive fazendo
Dialogue: 0,00:11:01.18,00:11:03.68,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,何をしていたんだ!?》
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:03.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,até agora?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:03.68,00:11:12.70,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:11:12.70,00:11:15.20,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(左近)フッフフフ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:11:15.20,00:11:17.71,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,いい目をしてる｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:17.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele tem um bom olhar.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:28.26,00:11:31.26,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:11:31.26,00:11:33.27,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,そろそろ行くか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:33.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos logo?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:33.27,00:11:42.72,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:11:42.72,00:11:44.22,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ぐっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:11:44.22,00:11:52.73,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:12:38.33,00:12:40.27,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,何のまねだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:40.87,Main,,0,0,0,,O que acha que está fazendo?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:40.27,00:12:43.27,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)こうでもしないとお前 逃げちゃうでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:43.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Se eu não fizer isso,\Nvocê vai fugir, não vai?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:43.27,00:12:47.28,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,おとなしく説教 聞くタイプじゃないからねぇ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:47.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Você não é do tipo que\Nouve as coisas em silêncio.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:49.28,00:12:52.79,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あいつは 確かコピー忍者のカカシぜよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:52.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Se me lembro bem,\Né o Kakashi, o ninja copiador.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:52.79,00:12:54.79,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,チッ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:12:54.79,00:12:57.30,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)サスケ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:59.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Sasuke, esqueça essa\Nhistória de vingança.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:57.30,00:12:59.30,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,復しゅうなんて やめとけ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:12:59.30,00:13:01.31,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,何？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:01.04,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,00:13:01.31,00:13:03.31,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)まっ こんな仕事柄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:06.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Bom, por aqui, vi\Nvários caras como você.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:03.31,00:13:06.32,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前のようなヤツは腐るほど見てきたが
Dialogue: 0,00:13:06.32,00:13:11.33,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,復しゅうを口にしたヤツの末路はろくなもんじゃない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:10.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas o fim daqueles que falam\Nsobre vingança nunca é bom.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:11.33,00:13:13.83,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,悲惨なもんだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.52,Main,,0,0,0,,São fins trágicos.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:16.34,00:13:21.35,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)今より もっと自分を傷つけ苦しむことになるだけだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:21.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Só vai se ferir e agonizar\Nainda mais que agora.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:21.35,00:13:23.85,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,たとえ 復しゅうに成功したとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:26.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que se vingue,\Ntudo o que restará será o vazio.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:23.85,00:13:25.86,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,残るのは むなしさだけだ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:13:25.86,00:13:28.86,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,黙れ！ あんたに何が分かる!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:27.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Calado!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:29.00,Main,,0,0,0,,O que você sabe?!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:28.86,00:13:31.87,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,知ったふうなことを俺の前で言ってんじゃねえよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:32.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Não fale comigo como\Nse soubesse de algo!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:31.87,00:13:34.37,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)まぁ 落ち着け｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:34.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Bom, calma...
Dialogue: 0,00:13:34.37,00:13:36.38,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,何なら 今から
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.94,0:13:36.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Se você quiser,
Dialogue: 0,00:13:36.38,00:13:39.82,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あんたのいちばん大事な人間を殺してやろうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:40.40,Main,,0,0,0,,posso ir matar a pessoa mais\Nimportante para você agora.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:39.82,00:13:42.82,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,今 あんたが言ったことがどれほど ズレてるか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:43.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Aí você vai perceber\Ncomo está errado
Dialogue: 0,00:13:42.82,00:13:44.83,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,実感できるぜ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:45.09,Main,,0,0,0,,sobre o que você falou!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:44.83,00:13:48.34,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)まっ そうしてもらっても結構だがな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:48.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Bom, eu não me importaria\Nse você fizesse isso.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:48.34,00:13:52.34,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あいにく 俺には 一人もそんなヤツは いないんだよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:52.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Infelizmente, nem tenho\Numa pessoa assim.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:53.85,00:13:57.35,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)もう みんな殺されてる｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:57.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Todos já estão mortos.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:59.36,00:14:01.86,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)俺も お前より長く生きてる｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:02.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu vivi mais que você...
Dialogue: 0,00:14:01.86,00:14:04.87,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,時代も悪かった｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:04.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Não foram bons tempos.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:04.87,00:14:09.37,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,失う苦しみは嫌ってほど知ってるよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:09.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Conheço muito bem a\Nagonia de perder alguém.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:12.38,00:14:15.89,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)まっ 俺も お前もラッキーなほうじゃない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:16.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Bom, nós dois não temos sorte.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:15.89,00:14:18.90,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,それは確かだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:18.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Disso tenho certeza.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:18.90,00:14:22.40,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,でも 最悪でもない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:21.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas também não somos os piores.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:22.40,00:14:24.41,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,俺にも お前にも
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:24.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Nós dois
Dialogue: 0,00:14:24.41,00:14:27.91,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,もう大切な仲間が見つかっただろ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:27.66,Main,,0,0,0,,encontramos companheiros queridos, não?
Dialogue: 0,00:14:27.91,00:14:33.93,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:14:33.93,00:14:36.93,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)失ってるからこそ分かる｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:37.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Consigo entender o que sente.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:36.93,00:14:40.87,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,千鳥は お前に大切なものができたからこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:39.04,Main,,0,0,0,,O Chidori é um poder
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:42.64,Main,,0,0,0,,que lhe dei porque agora\Nvocê possui algo importante.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:40.87,00:14:43.38,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,与えた力だ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:14:43.38,00:14:47.89,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,その力は 仲間に向けるものでも復しゅうに使うものでもない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:45.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Deveria saber que não é um poder
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:48.47,Main,,0,0,0,,para ser usado em algum\Ncompanheiro ou por vingança.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:47.89,00:14:52.40,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,何のために使う力かお前なら分かってるはずだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:52.55,Main,,0,0,0,,E tenho certeza de que sabe\Npara o que deve usá-lo.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:52.40,00:14:56.40,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,俺の言ってることがズレてるかどうか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:58.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Pense bem se concorda ou\Nnão com o que estou falando.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:56.40,00:14:58.41,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,よく考えろ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:15:08.43,00:15:12.44,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(鬼童丸)あれ並みの忍にウロウロされっとやりづれぇからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:12.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Será difícil com um ninja\Ndaquele nível por perto.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:12.44,00:15:14.94,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,少し待つぜよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:14.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Então vamos esperar um pouco.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:19.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Talvez idiotas como vocês não\Nconseguiriam. Mas {\i1}eu{\i0} consigo.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:14.94,00:15:17.95,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前らみたいなくそ野郎どもじゃダメでも
Dialogue: 0,00:15:17.95,00:15:19.95,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うちなら やれる｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:24.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Será? "Dois" devem ser o\Nbastante para acabar com ele.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:19.95,00:15:24.96,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,フッ どうかねぇ ２人いりゃ十分 バ～ラバラだけどよ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:15:24.96,00:15:28.47,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,いちいち口出しするなゲス野郎が｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.99,0:15:28.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Não se meta toda hora, maldito.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:28.47,00:15:30.47,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,チッ｡(次郎坊)多由也｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:32.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Tayuya, mulheres não\Ndevem falar assim.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:30.47,00:15:32.48,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,女が そういうことばをあんまり…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:15:32.48,00:15:34.48,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うるせぇよ デブ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:34.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Calado, gordão.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:50.95,00:16:00.96,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:16:10.99,00:16:21.00,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:16:31.03,00:16:41.04,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:16:44.49,00:16:46.49,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜お代わり！＞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:46.19,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Mais, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:46.49,00:16:48.50,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜ん！＞＜ん～！＞
Dialogue: 0,00:16:48.50,00:16:52.00,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜タァ～！ ハァ ハァ…＞
Dialogue: 0,00:16:52.00,00:16:55.01,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:16:55.01,00:16:57.51,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜帰るか＞＜おう！＞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:56.56,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Quer voltar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:57.64,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Claro!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:57.51,00:17:00.02,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜デッヘヘヘ… ２人とも
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:02.75,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Nós dois chegamos ao topo da árvore.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:00.02,00:17:03.02,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,てっぺんまで登ったぜ＞
Dialogue: 0,00:17:03.02,00:17:13.03,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:17:16.05,00:17:18.05,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,おっ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:17:23.57,00:17:25.57,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,サクラちゃん｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:24.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:25.57,00:17:28.07,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あんたに少し話があるの｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:28.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Quero falar com você.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:30.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Vu sair com você,\Nentão venha junto.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:28.07,00:17:31.08,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,デートしてあげるからちょっと つきあいなさいよ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:17:52.06,00:17:54.06,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,チクショ～…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:53.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Droga...
Dialogue: 0,00:17:56.06,00:17:58.07,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,チクショ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:58.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,00:18:07.59,00:18:17.60,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:18:26.12,00:18:30.63,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《中忍試験の時に大蛇丸に付けられた呪印》
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:30.43,Italics,,0,0,0,,A marca da maldição deixada pelo\NOrochimaru no exame Chunin...
Dialogue: 0,00:18:30.63,00:18:38.65,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:18:38.65,00:18:43.09,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《カカシ先生は もう大丈夫だって言ってたけど…》
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:42.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,O Kakashi falou que\Nestava tudo bem, mas...
Dialogue: 0,00:18:43.09,00:18:53.10,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:18:58.62,00:19:01.13,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶﾌﾞﾄ)大蛇丸様｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:00.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:05.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Você não precisava mandar\Nos quatro, precisava?
Dialogue: 0,00:19:01.13,00:19:05.14,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,何も ４人全員を行かせなくてもよかったんじゃないですか？
Dialogue: 0,00:19:05.14,00:19:07.64,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(大蛇丸)あの子たち みんな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.64,0:19:11.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Parece que aquelas crianças estão\Ninteressadas no Sasuke como eu.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:07.64,00:19:11.65,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,私が気に入ってるサスケ君に興味があるみたいね｡
Dialogue: 0,00:19:11.65,00:19:14.65,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,一体 どれほどの力なのか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:14.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Para ver o quão grande seu poder é...
Dialogue: 0,00:19:14.65,00:19:17.16,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶﾌﾞﾄ)力比べも何も
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:16.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Uma prova de poder ou algo assim...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:20.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Agora o Sasuke não\Nseria páreo para eles.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:17.16,00:19:20.17,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,今のサスケ君ぐらいでは相手にもならないでしょう｡
Dialogue: 0,00:19:20.17,00:19:24.17,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(大蛇丸)フッフッフッフッ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:19:24.17,00:19:26.18,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,だからこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:29.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Por isso mesmo, ele virá\Naté mim à procura de poder.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:26.18,00:19:30.19,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,すぐにでも私に力を求めてくるのよ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:19:30.19,00:19:36.20,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:19:36.20,00:19:39.20,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,何者だ？ お前ら｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:38.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem são vocês?
Dialogue: 0,00:19:39.20,00:19:43.71,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,音の四人衆 東門の鬼童丸｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:43.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Sou Kidomaru, o Portal Leste\Ndo Quarteto do Som.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:43.71,00:19:46.22,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,同じく西門の左近｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:46.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Sou Sakon, Portal Oeste.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:46.22,00:19:49.22,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,同じく南門の次郎坊｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:49.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu sou Jirobo, o Portal Sul.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:49.22,00:19:52.23,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,同じく北門の多由也｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:51.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Sou Tayuya, Portal Norte.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:52.23,00:20:02.24,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:20:02.75,00:20:04.75,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(鬼童丸)ダッ！
Dialogue: 0,00:20:04.75,00:20:09.76,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:20:09.76,00:20:11.77,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:20:11.77,00:20:13.77,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:20:13.77,00:20:16.28,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ドリャ～！
Dialogue: 0,00:20:16.28,00:20:18.28,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(鬼童丸)どわっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:20:18.28,00:20:20.29,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,オラ～！(次郎坊)あっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:20:20.29,00:20:30.30,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:20:34.81,00:20:36.32,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あっ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:20:36.32,00:20:46.33,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:56.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Agora não estou de bom humor...
Dialogue: 0,00:20:54.29,00:20:57.29,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,俺は今 機嫌が悪いんだ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:20:57.29,00:20:59.80,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,これ以上やるってんなら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:20:59.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Se quiserem lutar,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:01.32,Main,,0,0,0,,não vou pegar leve!
Dialogue: 0,00:20:59.80,00:21:01.80,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,手加減しねえぜ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:21:41.35,00:21:46.86,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬(ｴﾝﾃﾞｨﾝｸﾞﾃｰﾏ)
Dialogue: 0,00:21:46.86,00:21:50.37,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ ごくたまに
Dialogue: 0,00:21:50.37,00:21:54.37,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 僕たまに
Dialogue: 0,00:21:54.37,00:21:59.88,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 夢に破れるひとのカケラが
Dialogue: 0,00:21:59.88,00:22:05.33,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ ヤマのように見える
Dialogue: 0,00:22:05.33,00:22:08.33,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:22:08.33,00:22:11.84,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 神様に
Dialogue: 0,00:22:11.84,00:22:15.85,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 仏様に
Dialogue: 0,00:22:15.85,00:22:21.36,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ すがり泣いているひとのカケラが
Dialogue: 0,00:22:21.36,00:22:25.37,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ ヤマのように見える
Dialogue: 0,00:22:25.37,00:22:26.87,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:22:26.87,00:22:29.88,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ ダンランダンスでランデブー
Dialogue: 0,00:22:29.88,00:22:34.39,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 俺 勝利のﾎﾟｰｽﾞだﾗﾝﾀﾞﾗﾝ(round around)
Dialogue: 0,00:22:34.39,00:22:36.89,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ シェイク シェイク探そうじゃない
Dialogue: 0,00:22:36.89,00:22:41.40,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 終わらないバイバイのリズムで
Dialogue: 0,00:22:41.40,00:22:49.92,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:22:49.92,00:22:55.43,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ ヤマのように見える…
Dialogue: 0,00:22:55.43,00:22:56.93,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:22:56.93,00:23:00.44,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ ヤマのように見える…
Dialogue: 0,00:23:00.44,00:23:03.95,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ ヤマのように見える…
Dialogue: 0,00:23:03.95,00:23:08.95,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ ヤマのように見える…
Dialogue: 0,00:23:11.89,00:23:15.90,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,〈デート！ デート！サクラちゃん 何 食べたい？〉
Dialogue: 0,00:23:15.90,00:23:18.91,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,〈何でもいい〉〈にしても カカシ先生ってば
Dialogue: 0,00:23:18.91,00:23:22.42,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,大げさだよな 俺 ちょっとｻｽｹとやってみたかっただけなのによ〉
Dialogue: 0,00:23:22.42,00:23:25.42,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,〈でも カカシ先生が止めてなかったら 今頃…〉
Dialogue: 0,00:23:25.42,00:23:29.93,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,〈もっちろん！ どっちが強いか決着がついてたってばよ！〉
Dialogue: 0,00:23:29.93,00:23:31.93,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,〈ねぇ 聞いて ナルト〉
Dialogue: 0,00:23:34.44,00:23:36.94,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,〈私 胸騒ぎがするの…〉
Dialogue: 0,00:23:51.47,00:23:56.15,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,≪(六花の泣き声)
Dialogue: 0,00:23:56.15,00:23:59.49,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(六花)やっぱり 私 まだ
Dialogue: 0,00:23:59.49,00:24:02.49,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,島尾君のことが…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:24:02.49,00:24:07.50,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(六花の泣き声)
